history.content:
There's no doubt that all of these will be mostly or completely full during phase 1. Think about which you find as a priority. What you want to study (theory? AI? communications?), and which path is most related (e.g. what future upper divs you want to take).

Also look at the professors.

In the end, if you have more semester, it almost does not matter. You have time to take them all.
